      <title>欧元区财长承诺削减支出以减少债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/euro-area-finance-chiefs-commit-to-spending-cuts-to-reduce-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区各国政府承诺明年削减支出，以减少借贷。此前多年来，欧元区各国政府一直加大支出，支持企业和家庭度过新冠疫情和能源危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/euro-area-finance-chiefs-commit-to-spending-cuts-to-reduce-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:42:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CoinShares 称比特币投资产品连续第三周流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bitcoin-investment-products-see-third-straight-week-of-inflows-coinshares-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 CoinShares Ltd. 的数据，上周比特币投资产品流入 13.5 亿美元，为连续第三周流入，创下 6 月初以来的最高流入额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bitcoin-investment-products-see-third-straight-week-of-inflows-coinshares-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>低评级 CLO ETF 规模首次超过 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一只购买低评级担保贷款债务（CLO）敞口的交易所交易基金的资产规模已超过 10 亿美元，这对于曾经仅对机构投资者开放的市场中快速增长的 CLO 基金而言又是一个里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果被摩根士丹利评为首选股 再创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/apple-is-top-pick-at-morgan-stanley-as-ai-seen-driving-iphone-ipad-upgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 周一再创新高，此前这家科技巨头被摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 列为首选股票。摩根士丹利认为，苹果人工智能平台的推出引发了用户升级智能手机、平板电脑和电脑的新一轮热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/apple-is-top-pick-at-morgan-stanley-as-ai-seen-driving-iphone-ipad-upgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯公司将以 28 亿美元收购加拿大 Stelco 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司 (Cleveland-Cliffs Inc.) 同意以约 38.5 亿加元（28 亿美元）收购加拿大钢铁制造商 Stelco Holdings Inc.，这是该公司在去年竞购美国钢铁公司失败后的首次重大举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚顶级银行计划出售 2.46 亿美元股份以获取资本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/top-nigeria-lender-plans-246-million-share-sale-to-boost-gtbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[担保信托控股公司 (Guaranty Trust Holding Co.) 计划通过出售股票筹集 2.462 亿美元，为其尼日利亚子公司注入更多资本，这是自 3 月份尼日利亚央行提高该行业的资本门槛以来，贷款机构最关注的一家公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/top-nigeria-lender-plans-246-million-share-sale-to-boost-gtbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:36:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>焦点：中国数据令油价低迷 贸易局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估了美国和中国需求低迷的迹象，油价小幅走低，而随着市场消化了对唐纳德·特朗普的攻击并展望收益，股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数创下新高，长期债券价格下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀袭击增加了他入主白宫的可能性，但有关市场波动加剧的呼声并未成为现实，股市因此升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员消化最新地缘政治冲击，美国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-steady-as-traders-digest-latest-geopolitial-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡周末唐纳德·特朗普遇袭事件对市场的影响并期待本周的财报热潮，美国股市周一开盘走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-steady-as-traders-digest-latest-geopolitial-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后乐观情绪推动加密货币价格上涨，比特币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对暗杀企图作出坚决回应，引发人们猜测这位支持加密货币的前总统赢得连任的机会有所增加，随后比特币出现了近两个月来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
